1. get taglib + compile
2. get php source (apt-get source php5)
3. go to ext/ dir
4. git clone taglib-php
5. phpize
6. ./configure
7. Edit Makefile: CXXFLAGS= -std=c++11
8. ./build.sh --quick --no-tests
9. sudo cp modules/taglib.so /path/to/extension_dir (see extension_dir in your php.ini)
10. add extension=taglib.so to your php.ini


